Love on the Dark Side

Chapter 16 - Clash of minds

Gathering the dark Force around him, dragging it towards him, into his very soul until it utterly pervaded him, he stretched out his hand and unleashed it on the general.

The next moment Hux was pressed against the wall near the door, unable to make one move. Kylo stood there, dark shadows in his burning eyes.
